summary: An ordinance relating to and authorizing the appropriation of a sum of money from the General Fund of the City of Seattle as a loan to the Local Improvement Fund Condemnation Award District No. 3749, created by Ordinance No. 46041, for the purpose of satisfying the judgement entered in condemnation case of Corson Avenue, under Ordinance No. 44985, Cause No. 168665.
